title: President Donald J. Trump Signs H.R. 339 into Law – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Economy & Jobs	

Issued on:
August 22, 2017
On Tuesday, August 22, 2017, the President signed into law:H.R. 339, the “Northern Mariana Islands Economic Expansion Act,” which makes certain changes to the transitional worker program for the Commonwealth of the Northern Mariana Islands.
